'''Dead Marshes''' can refer to: 
==Middle-earth==
* The '''[[Dead Marshes]]''', the wetlands that lay north-west of the [[Dagorlad]] and where [[Frodo]], [[Sam]] and [[Gollum]] found passage on their way to [[Mordor]].

==Adaptations==
* [[The Dead Marshes]], the eleventh track of disc one of ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers - The Complete Recordings]]'' by [[Howard Shore]].
* [[Dagorlad and the Dead Marshes]] is a module (in the Adventure-series) for [[Middle-earth Role Playing]], 1st Edition.
